Instructions how to extract and build the package using cabal
Run the following commands (requires cabal version >= 1.18)

cabal unpack shrdlite.tar.gz
cd shrdlite-0.1.0.0.tar.gz
cabal sandbox init
cabal install --only-dependencies
cabal configure
cabal build

The executable will be located in /dist/build/shrdlite/shrdlite


The documentation (and source code) is best viewed in a web browser
Open the file /doc/index.html
